<article id="node-221861" class="node node-blogs article odd node-full clearfix" about="/culture/2015/02/tracey-thorn-more-attention-we-pay-childish-behaviour-more-we-get" typeof="sioc:Item foaf:Document" role="article">

  <div class="node-inner">

    
              <header class="node-header">

                  <h1 property="dc:title" datatype="" class="node-title" rel="nofollow">
                          Tracey Thorn: The more attention we pay to childish behaviour, the more we get                      </h1>
              
      <h1 class="subheadline"><div class="field field-name-field-subheadline field-type-text-long field-label-hidden view-mode-full"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"> <p>
	Indulging childishness is why we’re stuck with Boris Johnson, Katie Hopkins and Jeremy Clarkson.</p>
 </div></div></div></h1>
         
      <span class="submitted">
      
                  <p class="submitted"><span property="dc:date dc:created" content="2015-02-05T14:47:48+00:00" datatype="xsd:dateTime" rel="sioc:has_creator">by <a href="/writers/71729" title="View user profile." class="username" xml:lang="" about="/users/tracey-thorn" typeof="sioc:UserAccount" property="foaf:name" datatype="">Tracey Thorn</a> <span class="published_date">Published <time datetime="2015-02-05T14:47:48+0000" pubdate="pubdate">5 February, 2015 - 14:47</time></span></span></p>
         
		
		      <nav class="clearfix"><ul class="links inline"><li class="widgets_service_links-default first last"><span><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A//www.newstatesman.com/culture/2015/02/tracey-thorn-more-attention-we-pay-childish-behaviour-more-we-get&amp;count=horizontal&amp;via=&amp;text=Tracey%20Thorn%3A%20The%20more%20attention%20we%20pay%20to%20childish%20behaviour%2C%20the%20more%20we%20get&amp;counturl=http%3A//www.newstatesman.com/culture/2015/02/tracey-thorn-more-attention-we-pay-childish-behaviour-more-we-get" class="twitter-share-button service-links-twitter-widget" title="Tweet This" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"><span class="element-invisible">Tweet Widget</span></a><a href="http://www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?href=http%3A//www.newstatesman.com/culture/2015/02/tracey-thorn-more-attention-we-pay-childish-behaviour-more-we-get&amp;layout=button_count&amp;show_faces=false&amp;action=like&amp;colorscheme=light&amp;width=90&amp;height=21&amp;font=&amp;locale=" title="I Like it" class="service-links-facebook-like" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"><span class="element-invisible">Facebook Like</span></a><a href="http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A//www.newstatesman.com/culture/2015/02/tracey-thorn-more-attention-we-pay-childish-behaviour-more-we-get&amp;title=Tracey%20Thorn%3A%20The%20more%20attention%20we%20pay%20to%20childish%20behaviour%2C%20the%20more%20we%20get" title="Submit this post on reddit.com" class="service-links-reddit" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"><img typeof="foaf:Image" class="image-style-none" src="http://www.newstatesman.com/sites/all/modules/service_links/images/reddit.png" alt="Reddit logo" /></a><a href="http://www.stumbleupon.com/submit?url=http%3A//www.newstatesman.com/culture/2015/02/tracey-thorn-more-attention-we-pay-childish-behaviour-more-we-get&amp;title=Tracey%20Thorn%3A%20The%20more%20attention%20we%20pay%20to%20childish%20behaviour%2C%20the%20more%20we%20get" title="Thumb this up at StumbleUpon" class="service-